reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits Small Adults
reviews.reviewText: This set of headphones is for children but they do fit small adults. They are well made… and I am very pleased with how comfortable they are. The sound is great too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durable headphones for children
reviews.reviewText: This is our second pair of these headphones. My 3 year old is NOT easy on them! He drags them, throws them, smashes them, and basically abuses them! For the price, they’re pretty fantastic! Have a long cord and nice padding on the ear pieces. Good sound quality and still work even if the ear pieces are broken off! My sons are currently being held together with nail glue and a prayer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Grandson uses them for school, he asked for this brand.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cost Effective But Don’t Last Long
reviews.reviewText: Love the colors and price on these which is why I bought them for my girls (5, 7, 9). We purchased these at the beginning of the school year (Aug 2022) and already two of the three that we bought are no longer working (the five-year-old has only used them twice, so definitely not enough times for them to have run their course). They are the right size for my kids so, it’s worth the cost to find some thing that fits well for our kiddos. Very cute colors and they do the trick for little ears but buyer beware if you’re looking for something to keep for years and years this isn’t the one.

reviews.reviewTitle: Surprised at how good they are
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for my 6 year old to use on road trips and so far I am really impressed. I tried them myself and they are really comfy and sound great. They were a replacement for dollar store headphones we used to have and they are a huge improvement. I think they are even better than the headphones her sister uses that cost twice as much. I might even order a second pair of my own.
Acheter pour kon garçon de 6 ans et je suis agréablement surpris. Fonctionne bien et sont très beau en plus

reviews.reviewTitle: Overall a nice set of headphones
reviews.reviewText: These headphones are really cute for kids. My daughter loves them. They are colorful and comfortable. The sound quality is good and thankfully because it is directed towards kids they are not too loud. There should be no worries of hearing damage but the sound is still loud enough and clear enough to enjoy. Overall a nice set of headphones and recommended by my daughter.
